Why Choose Us

  • Safety
  • Quality
  • Efficiency

Our Priority in operating
our business is “SAFETY”,
We conduct Improvement
Continuously. We have 5 safety Procedures
and keep reminder each other with saying " GO ANZEN NI"
means "Jagalah Keselamatan"
and keeps "focus" on your steps and works.

Only trained and licensed (Certificated)
Personnel can operate the Crane. monitoring and maintain skill up
by conducting Training periodically.

With start Operating with all
High Accuracy Facilities and Equipments
keep maintaining output HIGH
ACCURACY FINISHED GOODS
as Customer's Requirement.

To avoid any Dust, insect, small animals
come in the Factory, all doors and windows
are always in closed condition.

To avoid any Dust, insect, small animals
come in the processing Material , provide Cover ,
on top of Processing Machinery.

Monitoring & Controlling the Process
productivity and efficiency By conducting
Improvement Activities

Warehouse with bathcontrol

Basic Ordering Methods

  • Ordering
  • Delivery
  • Packaging

Basic Transaction Flow:
Customer informs us the forecast in advance at least for next 3 months of demand.

Customer submit Purchase Order (P.O)
and Delivery Schedule to HSSI atleast 1 week before Delivery date
HSSI deliver the Goods based on Delivery Schedule (includes Scraps based on customer requirement)

HSSI issues invoice
Payment terms based on agreement both Parties.

Standard Safety Packing Max Weight 2 Ton/skid or Max Height 400mm (Total 500mm include Skid Height)
